data.description:
*New paint and new doors done after pictures*
This cozy 2 story townhome offers a great open concept floor plan. The main floor is all hardwood. The living is a good size and features a 3 sided gas fireplace. The kitchen has an island and new stainless steel appliances. The second floor features a large master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and private bath, two additional bedrooms, bathroom and a laundry closet. Washer and dryer are included. Newer AC unit and exterior paint. The back patio is great for entertaining with entry to the 2-car detached garage. Schedule a showing today!
